_json.gridTitle: Home Improvement Tips That Lead To Success Despite A Lack Of Knowledge – Remodeling Zone
_json.description: Even the most basic bath tub can be expensive. And when you are flipping homes, it's important to try to curb costs wherever possible while creating a superior product. My partner, Lance, came up with this tub trick and we've used it about 3 times now with extraordinary results.  As much as I want to keep all our secrets to ourselves, this one is so good and so easy that we just had to share it. Remodeling your bathroom but don't want to spend a fortune?
